snippet.title: Best VGM 1560 - Castlevania 64 - Clock Tower (Toothed Wheel)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 411 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUzLO2GpPv4
Best VGM 2195 - https://youtu.be/UPdZlmyedcI

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo 64
Castlevania 64 / Legacy of Darkness (1998)
Clock Tower (Toothed Wheel)
Masahiko Kimura, Motoaki Furukawa & Maiko Egawa
